@startuml
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam backgroundColor #F5F5F5
skinparam defaultFontSize 13
[*] --> Approved
Approved --> Draft : update
Approved : entry / log payment
Draft --> Reviewed : reject
Reviewed --> Rejected : confirm
Rejected --> Pending : confirm
Rejected : entry / log payment
Pending --> Archived : reject
Archived --> [*]
@enduml